headline: A Fresh Look at Affirm (AFRM) Valuation as Apple Pay and Wellness Partnerships Expand User Reach
summary: Affirm Holdings (AFRM) just pulled off a trifecta of partnerships that could reshape how people pay for everything from home repairs to spa treatments. The company’s direct integration with Apple Pay now lets iPhone users across the U.S. tap into flexible payments right at the point of sale. This widens Affirm’s reach into everyday purchases.
